title: PixelPerfect Pixel Perfect with Bert Monroy
description:
All the PixelPerfect Episodes in their highest resolution from Revision3 with Bert Monroy. Since his show has been canceled, I thought I do you a favor with this torrent.

Number of Episodes: 107

Unfortunatly I can't seed all day, because I will turn off my Computer during sleeping hours (about 8-9hrs) but the rest of the day I will most certainly seed!

I don't have that fast of a up-speed (about 90kb/s) so i guess by the end of the week there should be other seeders as well.

and don't forget, the more ppl. download different parts the better the downspeed will be, since everybody might have different parts but all together you have all parts of the download. but i guess you know that already ;)
